arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	--Play Wailing noise
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(ID_SPIRITSHRINE_TOWN, SFX_WAILING)
	

	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()

	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		if Hydra.ActorsInSameLevelArea(idActor, idPlayer) then
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPlayer) then
				Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idPlayer, SFX_TORMENTED_REMAINS_2CH)
			end
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(2.0)
	
	
	-- Get a refreshed referenced to the follower, since it can be invalidated at any time
	local idfollowerYorin = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_YORIN_FOLLOWER)
	
	-- Check validity, every time
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idfollowerYorin) == true then

		-- Check if the Follower is following the player that is triggering the callback
		if Hydra.ActorGetFollowTarget(idfollowerYorin) == idActor then
			
			--Yorin comments on Wailing noise
			Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_NOISE, idfollowerYorin)
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	--Disable Spirit spawner
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(SPN_SPIRITS_01) then
		Hydra.ActorDisable(SPN_SPIRITS_01)
	end
	
end

arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
followerYorin = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_YORIN_FOLLOWER)
bYorin = true
Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(idYorinSpawnLoc, followerYorin)
Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idYorinSpawnLoc, followerYorin)
	
	--Remove Yorrin Follower
	--if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerYorin) then
	--	Hydra.ActorDelete(followerYorin)
	--end
--Stop Combat music
Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent")

Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

arQuestPhases.szOnEnterScript:
--Activate Spirit Spawner for Tormented Shrine encounter
	Hydra.ActorEnable(SPN_SPIRITS_01)

--Play combat music
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Scosglen_Airidah_Phase1")

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	--Remove Yorrin Follower
	--if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerYorin) then
	--	Hydra.ActorDelete(followerYorin)
	--end
	--Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_YORIN)
	--Remove Vine Barriers linked to Arlo; Enable Breakable Barriers
	local tFog = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorNPC, "Fog")
	local tVines = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorNPC, "Breakables")
	
	--Remove Fog Barrier Vines
	for i, idFog in ipairs(tFog) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idFog)
	end
	
	--Enable Breakable Vines
	for i, idVines in ipairs(tVines) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idVines)
	end
	
--Enable Retreat volume in Clocheen
	Hydra.ActorEnable(TRIG_RETREAT)

-- Moved Yorin bark conversation out of background phase
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_YORIN_BARK, ID_YORIN)
	
end

function Start()

	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_YORIN)
		
	if bYorin then
		Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_YORIN, idYorinSpawnLoc)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_YORIN, idYorinSpawnLoc)
	end
		
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_YORIN, LOC_YORIN_SHRINE, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_YORIN, LOC_YORIN_SHRINE)
			
	--Yorin comments on destroyed Tormented Shrine
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_CLEAR_01, ID_YORIN)

	--Arlo and Maisie open hut door and enter the scene
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_ARLO)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(ID_ARLO, false)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_MAISIE)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_ARLO, "NPC_NonCombat_HTH_Suspicious") -- Start suspicious
		
	--Open Arlo's door
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_DOOR_HUT)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(ID_DOOR_HUT)
		
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_ARLO, LOC_ARLO_WALK, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_ARLO, LOC_ARLO_WALK)
		
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_MAISIE, LOC_MAISIE_WALK, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_MAISIE, LOC_MAISIE_WALK)

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Clear the animset override of 'suspicion'
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(ID_ARLO)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(ID_ARLO, true)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--Yorin comments on destroyed Tormented Shrine
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_CLEAR_02, ID_YORIN, ID_ARLO)
	
end

arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()

--Player comments on fog clearing, returing to Yorin
	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_CLEAR_BARK, tPlayers[i])
	end
	
	Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

--Yorin and Arlo Revelation Callout Conversation
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_REV_CALL, ID_YORIN)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
--Yorin looks at Arlo
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_YORIN) then
		Hydra.ActorFaceActor(ID_YORIN, ID_ARLO)
	end

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer, idParentNode)
	
--Yorin moves to Arlo
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_YORIN) then
		Hydra.ActorClearLoadout(ID_YORIN)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_YORIN, LOC_YORIN_WALK, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_YORIN, LOC_YORIN_WALK)
	end

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
--Enable optional conversations for Arlo and Maise
	clArlo = Hydra.ReferenceConversationList("NPC_QST_Scos_Arlo")
	clMaisie = Hydra.ReferenceConversationList("NPC_QST_Scos_Maisie")
	
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(ID_ARLO, clArlo)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(ID_MAISIE, clMaisie)

end
